{
  "stem": "27335.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I didn't know, I didn't know what to, what to do with the man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then came, then came another event what we're waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It came way up in 1985.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1985, the time came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the time when the Tories had the nationwide campaign, and that was the year when the [INAUDIBLE] government got in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in the Hungarian house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, on, on, on the Hungarian house is on, on St.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Clair Avenue.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It used to be a huge, huge synagogue, the Hungarian nationalist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that [INAUDIBLE], so Hungarian house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was this Tory meeting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I read, then, a couple days later, in the Hungarian right-wing paper, reporting about this meeting, because they were-- the editor of the paper was also a war criminal.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And never been exposed yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- but he died already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there are others here who are even bigger than [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even that, I wish I could-- but anyway, I wrote a report in, in my, in my paper that such and such a meeting took place in the Hungarian nationalist home, in the nationalist home, and who do I see among the names on the platform?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even from Winnipeg, they, they, they imported some kind of real outright rabid Polish nationalist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This kind of people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I named Hungarians that are outright the Arrow Cross party, ex-Arrow Cross members.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And among them, sitting, Egri Gyorgy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How come-- this is how I place it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How come, how come a Jew, probably the survivor of the Holocaust in Hungary, sitting among the most rabid right-wing politicians in, in, in the platform in a Hungarian, Hungarian house?",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
